{"tid":641784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多倫多車禍】疑兇行兇前fb神秘留言 「非自願單身者的叛逆」","createTime":"2018-04-25T09:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T09:20:15.000Z","uid":73276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a38a79a5a0836cd5e8b2abf96ded559948a5549","tid":641784,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"加拿大多倫多貨車蓄意撞人案，警方指疑兇行兇前數分鐘，在facebook神秘留言。<br />\n<br />\n多倫多警方高級探長吉布森（Graham Gibson）表示，25歲疑兇米納西安（Alek Minassian 圖左）行兇前幾分鐘，在facebook提到「incel rebellion」（非單叛逆）。在一些網上留言板，「incel」是「involuntary celibacy」的縮寫，意思是「非自願單身」。<br />\n<br />\n米納西安的貼文，亦談及2014年美國加州一宗六死襲擊案，當年兇徒羅杰（Elliot Rodger 圖右）在行兇前曾拍片，怨恨女性不接受他追求，揚言要「殺光女孩子」。米納西安貼文中讚他是「一流君子」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國毒撚仲恐怖過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab0510b0d535dd982d49e4281f5cfd998a7e7fc","tid":641784,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"原來係特登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b09754d0234d937d0fcfc6d2063fc9ca71ea58","tid":641784,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"不教渡陰山"},{"pid":"a1e65daa81ad385fdfb7d4a030175f63903bafe6","tid":641784,"uid":170159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"食檸檬食到傻撚咗"},{"pid":"7101bd15ac9a14809a89bdf912b15ba6d150f20f","tid":641784,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}